### Example 4: Update service adding new countries
PUT {{TekusChallenge.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/services/GUID_DEL_SERVICIO
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "GUID_DEL_SERVICIO",
  "name": "Desarrollo Web Frontend Actualizado",
  "hourlyRate": 48.00,
  "description": "Desarrollo de interfaces de usuario con React, Vue.js, Angular y Next.js.",
  "providerId": "22818AD1-2905-41C5-A03B-A7A3ED8E1683",
  "countryCodes": ["CO", "MX", "PE", "CL", "AR"]
}

###

### Note: ISO Alpha-2 Country Codes
# Countries are loaded from the external API https://restcountries.com
# Use 2-character ISO Alpha-2 codes, for example:
# - CO: Colombia
# - MX: México
# - PE: Perú
# - US: Estados Unidos
# - BR: Brasil
# - CL: Chile
# - AR: Argentina
# - ES: España

